FBIS3-35492 "drnes038_l_94004" FBIS-NES-94-038 Document Type:Daily Report 25 Feb 1994 ISRAEL Gunman Kills Over 50 Arabs at Hebron Mosque 25 Feb Perpetrator Identified as U.S. Immigrant TA2502114494 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 1100 GMT 25 Feb 94 TA2502114494 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Language: Hebrew Article Type:BFN [Text] The settler who this morning murdered the Arab worshipers in the Cave of the Patriarchs is Dr. Barukh Goldstein, a Qiryat Arba' doctor. Dr. Goldstein immigrated from the United States. He was a Kakh member and was its candidate to the Qiryat Arba' local elections. During the shooting spree, Dr. Goldstein wore his IDF [Israel Defense Forces] uniform with the insignia of his rank of captain in the military reserves. Dr. Goldstein was killed after the shooting, but it is not clear whether he committed suicide or the worshipers killed him.
